Unlocked the feeling of motion sickness for me ;-;
And yes, maybe I am exceptionally bad at this game, but I have never felt so frustrated rolling a ball or trying to figure out how to roll the ball.

Being completly honest - it's a great funny game with a bunch of really weird stuff, but the fiddly controls (and to some level the sensory overload) made it just too frustrating to enjoy.
